nodes.text: Wing 4 was the callsign of a Republic Rocket-jumper troopship that served during the Freedon Nadd Uprising.
Wing 4 delievered Republic rocket-jumpers to the battlefield on Onderon in 3998 BBY, when the Republic sent a fleet of ships to aid the besieged Jedi task force there.
Its rocket-troopers came down in the same area as the Krath Enchanter.
